{"id":29,"idInBook":5070,"chapterId":68,"bookId":1,"arabic":"حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ، حَدَّثَنَا شُعْبَةُ، وَهَمَّامٌ، عَنْ قَتَادَةَ، عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ، عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ، قَالَ رَأَيْتُهُ عَبْدًا يَعْنِي زَوْجَ بَرِيرَةَ‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"Narrated Ibn `Abbas:","text":"I saw him as a slave, (namely, Barira's husband)."},"hadithNumber":5070,"vol":6,"hadithId":29,"reference":"68:29","meta":{"id":"bukhari","length":7563,"totalChapters":97,"arabic":{"title":"صحيح البخاري","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":68,"bookId":1,"arabic":"كتاب الطلاق","english":"Divorce","startHadith":5042,"endHadith":5136,"totalHadiths":95},"version":{"name":"bukhari","title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","chapters":97}}